  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    BreadthFirstIterator, DepthFirstIterator, DFIterator, FlatIterator, PostOrderIterator

    public abstract class IRIterator<E extends Traversable>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<E>
    An iterator implementing this interface supports special versions of next.
